msgid "`PoolCreator` is also the way to set Vert.x options that cannot be expressed as configuration properties, such as `SqlConnectOptions.setPreparedStatementCacheSqlFilter(Predicate<String>)`."
msgstr "`PoolCreator` 也是设置那些无法通过配置属性表达的 Vert.x 选项的途径，例如 `SqlConnectOptions.setPreparedStatementCacheSqlFilter(Predicate<String>)` 。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/reactive-sql-clients.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Pipelining"
msgstr "流水线处理"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/reactive-sql-clients.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The PostgreSQL and MariaDB/MySQL clients support pipelining of queries at the connection level.\n"
"The feature consists in sending multiple queries on the same database connection without waiting for the corresponding responses."
msgstr "PostgreSQL 和 MariaDB/MySQL 客户端支持在连接层级上进行查询流水线处理。该功能允许在同一数据库连接上发送多个查询，而无需等待相应的响应。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/reactive-sql-clients.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In some use cases, query pipelining can improve database access performance."
msgstr "在某些使用场景中，查询管道化可以提高数据库访问性能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/reactive-sql-clients.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Here's an example for PostgreSQL:"
msgstr "以下是一个 PostgreSQL 的示例："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/reactive-sql-clients.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The maximum number of pipelined queries is configured with the `pipelining-limit` property:"
msgstr "管道化查询的最大数量通过 `pipelining-limit` 属性进行配置："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/reactive-sql-clients.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "By default, `pipelining-limit` is set to 256."
msgstr "默认情况下， `pipelining-limit` 的值设置为 256。"

